<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1274000' id='t-1274000'>and other team members -- all the time.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
21:27
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1276000' id='t-1276000'>Alfred Mann has set up this foundation</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1279000' id='t-1279000'>to advance this research</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1281000' id='t-1281000'>because he saw</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1283000' id='t-1283000'>there's no way venture capital would come in for something like this.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1286000' id='t-1286000'>The audience is too small.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1288000' id='t-1288000'>You'd think, there's plenty of paralyzed people in the world,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1290000' id='t-1290000'>but the audience is too small,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1292000' id='t-1292000'>and the amount of research, the time it takes,</span>
